attributes.Long form description: The student changes the GoPro battery with a new one, then the instructor tells him to change the SD card with another one. At the end of this action asks to turn the GoPro on and off. After turning off the GoPro, the student mounts the black strap on the GoPro, when finished they tell him to remove it and replace it with the handheld grip; at the end he has to disassemble it. He finally places the GoPro on the table and ends the recording.
